## Impact Statements  

<|ref|>text<|/ref|><|det|>[[88, 109, 472, 214]]<|/det|>
Impact StatementsIn this study, we define the goals of prompt injection attacks and introduce an optimization- based strategy for conducting such attacks. Our research illuminates the previously underestimated security implications for language processing systems facing optimization- based prompt injection attacks. We hope our work can raise the awareness of the community to design effective defense strategies against such attacks.  

